trans-unit.source: Encapsulates the HTTP intrinsic object that provides access to files that were uploaded by a client.
trans-unit.target: 封裝提供用戶端所上傳檔案之存取權的 HTTP 內建函式物件。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.HttpFileCollectionWrapper> class derives from the <xref:System.Web.HttpFileCollectionBase> class and serves as a wrapper for the <xref:System.Web.HttpFileCollection> class.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.HttpFileCollectionWrapper>類別衍生自<xref:System.Web.HttpFileCollectionBase>類別，並做為包裝函式<xref:System.Web.HttpFileCollection>類別。

trans-unit.source: This class exposes the functionality of the <xref:System.Web.HttpFileCollection> class while also exposing the <xref:System.Web.HttpFileCollectionBase> type.
trans-unit.target: 這個類別會公開的功能<xref:System.Web.HttpFileCollection>類別也公開時<xref:System.Web.HttpFileCollectionBase>型別。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.HttpFileCollectionBase> class enables you to replace the original implementation of the <xref:System.Web.HttpFileCollection> class in your application with a custom implementation, such as when you perform unit testing outside the ASP.NET pipeline.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.HttpFileCollectionBase>類別可讓您取代的原始實作<xref:System.Web.HttpFileCollection>並用自訂的實作，例如，當您執行單元測試的 ASP.NET 管線外的應用程式中的類別。

trans-unit.source: The object that this wrapper class provides access to.
trans-unit.target: 由這個包裝函式提供存取的物件。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.HttpFileCollectionWrapper" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.Web.HttpFileCollectionWrapper" /> 類別的新執行個體。

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="httpApplicationState" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="httpApplicationState" /> 為 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: Gets an array that contains the keys (names) of all posted file objects in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 取得陣列，這個陣列包含集合中所有張貼檔案物件的索引鍵 (名稱)。

trans-unit.source: An array of file names.
trans-unit.target: 檔案名稱的陣列。

trans-unit.source: The one-dimensional array that is the destination of the elements copied from the collection.
trans-unit.target: 從集合複製項目之目的端一維陣列。

trans-unit.source: The array must have zero-based indexing.
trans-unit.target: 陣列必須有以零為起始的索引。

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index in <c>array</c> at which copying starts.
trans-unit.target: <c>array</c> 中以零為起始的索引，會從該處開始複製。

trans-unit.source: Copies the elements of the collection to an array, starting at the specified index in the array.
trans-unit.target: 從陣列中指定的索引處開始，將集合的項目複製到陣列。

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="array" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="array" /> 為 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="index" /> is less than zero.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="index" /> 小於零。

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="array" /> is multidimensional.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="array" /> 是多維的。

trans-unit.source: -or-

The number of elements in the source <see cref="T:System.Web.HttpFileCollectionWrapper" /> object is greater than the available space from <paramref name="index" /> to the end of the destination array.
trans-unit.target: 來源 <see cref="T:System.Web.HttpFileCollectionWrapper" /> 物件中的項目數，大於目的陣列從 <paramref name="index" /> 到結尾的可用空間。

trans-unit.source: The type of the source <see cref="T:System.Web.HttpFileCollectionWrapper" /> object cannot be cast automatically to the type of the destination array.
trans-unit.target: 來源 <see cref="T:System.Web.HttpFileCollectionWrapper" /> 物件的類型無法自動轉換成目的陣列的類型。

trans-unit.source: Gets the number of objects in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 取得集合中的物件數目。

trans-unit.source: The number of objects in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 集合中的物件數目。

trans-unit.source: Returns a posted file object from the collection by either name or index.
trans-unit.target: 依名稱或索引，傳回集合中已張貼的檔案物件。

trans-unit.source: The index of the item to return.
trans-unit.target: 所要傳回項目的索引。

trans-unit.source: Returns the posted file object at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: 傳回指定索引處所張貼的檔案物件。

trans-unit.source: The posted file object specified by <paramref name="index" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="index" /> 所指定的已張貼檔案物件。

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="index" /> is outside the valid range of indexes for the collection.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="index" /> 超出集合索引的有效範圍。

trans-unit.source: The name of the object to return.
trans-unit.target: 要傳回之物件的名稱。

trans-unit.source: Returns the posted file object that has the specified name from the collection.
trans-unit.target: 從集合中傳回具有指定名稱的已張貼檔案物件。

trans-unit.source: The posted file object specified by <paramref name="name" />, if found; otherwise, <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果找到則為 <paramref name="name" /> 所指定之已張貼檔案物件，否則為 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: Returns an enumerator that can be used to iterate through the collection.
trans-unit.target: 傳回列舉值，可用來逐一查看集合。

trans-unit.target: 可用於逐一查看集合的物件。

trans-unit.target: 要傳回之物件名稱的索引。

trans-unit.target: 傳回指定索引處所張貼檔案物件的名稱。

trans-unit.source: The name of the posted file object that is specified by <paramref name="index" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="index" /> 指定之已張貼檔案物件的名稱。

trans-unit.target: 傳回符合指定名稱的所有檔案。

trans-unit.target: 符合指定的名稱的檔案。

trans-unit.source: The information that is required in order to serialize the <see cref="T:System.Web.HttpFileCollectionWrapper" /> object.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether access to the collection is thread-safe.
trans-unit.target: 取得值，指出對集合的存取是否為安全執行緒。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if access is synchronized (thread-safe); otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果存取是同步的 (安全執行緒)，則為 <see langword="true" />，否則為 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: The default is <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 預設值為 <see langword="false" />。
